Notes


  • Characters that randomize into the Soldier class can promote into a Paladin or General using a Knight's Crest or Master Seal.
  • Characters that randomize into the Eirika Lord class can promote using a Knight's Crest or Master Seal.
  • Characters that randomize into the Ephraim Lord class can promote using a Knight's Crest or Master Seal.
  • Characters that randomize into Revenant, Sword/Lance Bonewalkers, and Mauthe Doogs promote using a Hero's Crest or Master Seal.
  • Characters that randomize into Tarvos and Bael promote using a Knight's Crest or Master Seal.
  • Characters that randomize into a Mogall promote using a Guiding Ring or Master Seal.
  • Characters that randomize into a Bow Bonewalker promote using an Orion's Bolt or Master Seal.
  • Characters that randomize into a Gargoyle promote using an Elysian Whip or Master Seal.
